@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container mt-5">
    <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
    <p class="text-muted">Last updated: October 2025</p>

    <hr />

    <h4>1. About HomeCare</h4>
    <p>
        HomeCare is a digital platform designed to make everyday healthcare tasks easier.
        We help users book home visits, manage appointments, and stay connected with their caregivers.
    </p>

    <h4>2. What data we collect</h4>
    <p>
        We collect basic user information such as name, email address, and contact details
        when you sign up or book a service. We do <strong>not</strong> share this information
        with third parties unless required by law.
    </p>

    <h4>3. How we protect your data</h4>
    <p>
        Your personal information is stored securely in our database and is only accessible to authorized staff.
        We use SSL encryption for all communication between your browser and our servers.
    </p>

    <h4>4. Cookies</h4>
    <p>
        HomeCare uses cookies to remember your preferences and improve your user experience.
        You can disable cookies in your browser settings at any time.
    </p>

    <h4>5. Contact us</h4>
    <p>
        If you have any questions about your privacy, please contact our support team at
        <a href="mailto:support@homecare.no">support@homecare.no</a>.
    </p>
</div>